ities%20of%20smallholder%20farmers.%20This%20is%20where%20%E2%80%98SEMA%20Alto%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20short%20for%20%E2%80%98Solar-powered%20Efficient%20Machinery%20for%20Agriculture%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20steps%20in.%20Founded%20in%202017%20in%20Bengaluru%20by%20co-founders%20Assad%20Jaffer%20and%20Dania%20Athar%2C%20the%20company%20was%20created%20to%20build%20clean%20energy%20and%20agri-tech%20solutions%20that%20lower%20costs%2C%20cut%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20and%20empower%20rural%20communities%20to%20keep%20more%20value%20from%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20retrofitting%20bulky%20diesel%20mills%20that%20were%20never%20suited%20to%20villages%2C%20SEMA%20reimagined%20the%20process%20entirely.%20The%20result%20was%20a%20decentralised%2C%20solar-compatible%20rice%20mill%3A%20compact%2C%20modular%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F269716%2Fslug-best-electric-vehicle-battery-india-startup-royal-ev-low-costslug-best-electric-vehicle-battery-india-startup-royal-ev-low-cost%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffordable%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20maintain%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Farmers%20could%20now%20process%20their%20paddy%20locally%2C%20on%20demand%2C%20instead%20of%20depending%20on%20distant%20and%20inefficient%20mills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20have%20to%20travel%20long%20distances%20to%20access%20large%20mills%20and%20do%20not%20have%20full%20control%20over%20how%20or%20when%20their%20paddy%20is%20processed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Assad%20explains.%20SEMA%E2%80%99s%20solution%20puts%20that%20power%20back%20in%20the%20village%2C%20providing%20an%20energy-efficient%2C%20farmer-first%20machine%20that%20can%20work%20with%20small%20batches.%20This%20approach%20reduces%20transport%20hassles%2C%20prevents%20losses%2C%20and%20cuts%20operational%20costs.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20integrating%20solar%20energy%20makes%20the%20solution%20both%20sustainable%20and%20aligned%20with%20India%E