adu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20supports%20farmers%20to%20package%20and%20sell%20rice%20of%20higher%20quality%20and%20at%20improved%20margins.%20For%20farmers%20like%20Gopi%2C%20this%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20machine.%20It%20marks%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20their%20agricultural%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20bridge%20that%20took%20innovation%20to%20the%20fields%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20SEMA%20designed%20the%20hardware%2C%20bringing%20it%20to%20scale%20required%20bridges%20beyond%20technology.%20The%20Council%20on%20Energy%2C%20Environment%20and%20Water%20(CEEW)%2C%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20this%20process%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Abhishek%20Jain%2C%20Director%20of%20Green%20Economy%20and%20Impact%20Innovations.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20its%20%E2%80%98Powering%20Livelihoods%E2%80%99%20initiative%2C%20a%20collaboration%20with%20Villgro%20(a%20social%20enterprise%20incubator)%2C%20CEEW%20helped%20unlock%20financing%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F403004%2Fstage-4-cancer-survivor-ride-of-hope-spreading-awareness-about-cancer-early-detection%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraise%20awareness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20link%20innovations%20like%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20to%20government%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInnovations%20like%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20often%20remain%20isolated%20if%20they%20do%20not%20connect%20with%20the%20right%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek.%20%E2%80%9COur%20role%20was%20to%20create%20those%20connections%2C%20making%20sure%20these%20technologies%20reach%20the%20farmers%20who%20need%20them%20most%2C%20backed%20by%20appropriate%20finance%2C%20supportive%20policy%2C%20and%20local%20demonstration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECEEW%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20were%20crucial%20in%20enabling%20end-user%20financing%20options%20for%20farmers%20who%20lacked%20collateral.%20They%20also%20organised%20demonstrations%20within%20villages%20to%20build%20trust%20and%20show%20the%20value%20of%20the%20mills%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20worked%20closely%20with%20financial%20institutions%20to%20introduce%20mechanisms%20like%20First%20Loss%20Default%20Guarantees.%20These%20tools%20reduce%20the%20risk%20lenders%20face%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20farmers%20with%20limited%20assets%20to%20access%20credit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192212.934_11zon-1755870749.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CEEW%20helps%20unlock%20financing%2C%20raise%20awareness%2C%20and%20link%20innovations%20like%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20to%20government%20schemes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192212.934_11zon-1755870749.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192212.934_11zon-1755870749-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192212.934_11zon-1755870749-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192212.934_11zon-1755870749-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192212.934_11zon-1755870749-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-490943%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECEEW%20helps%20unlock%20financing%2C%20raise%20awareness%2C%20and%20link%20innovations%20like%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20to%20government%20schemes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20finance%2C%20CEEW%20also%20pushed%20for%20policy%20recognition.%20They%20successfully%20advocated%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%20renewable-powered%20processing%20equipment%20in%20national%20programmes%20such%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Formalisation%20of%20Micro%20Food%20Processing%20Enterprises%20(PM-FME)%20scheme.%20This%20opened%20access%20to%20subsidies%20and%20loans%20for%20farmers%2C%20making%20adoption%20more%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20included%20in%20the%20PM-FME%20scheme%20marked%20a%20breakthrough%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abhishek%20emphasises.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20provided%20financial%20backing%20and%20gave%20official%20recognition%20to%20decentralised%20solar-powered%20processors%2C%20opening%20doors%20for%20mass%20adoption%20and%20long-term%20sustainability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20paddy%20to%20polished%20rice%3A%20Step-by-step%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20secret%20behind%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%E2%80%99%20success%20lies%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F252342%2Fomkar-thale-convert-petrol-electric-vehicle-activa-retrofit-innovation-arai-icat-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarefully%20engineered%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20protects%20grain%20quality%20while%20maximising%20yield.%20Every%20stage%20of%20the%20process%20is%20built%20for%20precision%20and%20efficiency%2C%20producing%20cleaner%2C%20more%20polished%20rice%20with%20minimal%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20begins%20with%20the%20pre-cleaner%2C%20which%20removes%20straw%2C%20chaff%2C%20and%20light%20impurities%20from%20raw%20paddy.%20This%20ensures%20that%20only%20clean%20grain%20enters%20the%20mill%2C%20protecting%20the%20machinery%20and%20improving%20downstream%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20the%20de-stoner%20removes%20heavier%20debris%20such%20as%20stones%20that%20could%20damage%20the%20equipment%20or%20contaminate%20the%20rice.%20With%20this%20step%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20final%20product%20is%20preserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192311.939_11zon-1755870809.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20secret%20behind%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills'%20success%20lies%20in%20their%20carefully%20engineered%20design%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192311.939_11zon-1755870809.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192311.939_11zon-1755870809-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192311.939_11zon-1755870809-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192311.939_11zon-1755870809-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192311.939_11zon-1755870809-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-490945%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20secret%20behind%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%E2%80%99%20success%20lies%20in%20their%20carefully%20engineered%20design%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paddy%20then%20moves%20to%20the%20triple-roller%20rubber%20sheller%2C%20the%20mill%E2%80%99s%20most%20distinctive%20feature.%20Driven%20by%20a%20single%20motor%2C%20three%20rollers%20are%20arranged%20in%20a%20triangular%20layout%20so%20that%20each%20kernel%20passes%20through%20twice%20in%20a%20dual-pass%20sequence.%20This%20doubles%20hulling%20efficiency%20while%20conserving%20energy%2C%20ensuring%20more%20complete%20husk%20removal%20without%20breaking%20the%20grain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20hulled%2C%20a%20separator%20isolates%20the%20brown%20rice%20from%20any%20remaining%20husk%2C%20giving%20farmers%20a%20cleaner%20output%20to%20send%20forward%20for%20polishing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grains%20then%20pass%20through%20a%20semi-polisher%20followed%20by%20a%20full-polisher.%20These%20stages%20refine%20the%20rice%20gradually%2C%20enhancing%20both%20its%20appearance%20and%20shelf%20life%2C%20while%20still%20preserving%20grain%20integrity%20%E2%80%94%20an%20essential%20factor%20for%20market%20acceptance.%20The%20grader%20completes%20the%20process%20by%20sorting%20grains%20by%20size%20to%20guarantee%20uniformity%20before%20packaging%2C%20which%20is%20critical%20for%20consumer%20appeal%20and%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mill%E2%80%99s%20components%20are%20arranged%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwaterfall%E2%80%9D%20layout%20that%20uses%20gravity%20to%20move%20the%20grain%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F400861%2Fgujarat-engineer-innovates-solar-tiles-trees-to-promote-renewable-energy-tackle-space-constraints%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereducing%20power%20needs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Constructed%20entirely%20from%20food-grade%20stainless%20steel%2C%20the%20system%20meets%20hygiene%20standards%20and%20ensures%20the%20rice%20is%20fit%20for%20certification%20and%20sale