are%20companies%20like%20Microsoft%20'purely'%20with%20AI.%20He's%20calling%20it%20'Macrohard.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20is%20pictured%20at%20Cannes%20Lions%20in%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a90051a17a8c5b40535eb1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20Tesla%20signed%20a%20semiconductor%20deal%20with%20Samsung%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20wrote%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bwalk%20the%20line%20personally%20to%20accelerate%20the%20pace%20of%20progress.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMarc%20Piasecki%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20that%20his%20AI%20venture%2C%20xAI%2C%20is%20working%20to%20simulate%20software%20companies%20like%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe's%20said%20on%20X%20that%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bpurely%20AI%20software%20company%20called%20Macrohard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20said%20it%20should%20be%20possible%20since%20companies%20like%20Microsoft%20don't%20make%20physical%20hardware.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20he%20wants%20to%20%26quot%3Bsimulate%26quot%3B%20software%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20only%20artificial%20intelligence.%20He's%20even%20got%20a%20name%20for%20the%20new%20venture%3A%20Macrohard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20in%20a%20Friday%20X%20post%20that%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-artificial-intelligence-chatbot-elon-musk-xai-explained-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20startup%2C%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20building%20a%20%26quot%3Bpurely%20AI%20software%20company%20called%20Macrohard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20name%2C%20but%20the%20project%20is%20very%20real!%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20principle%2C%20given%20that%20software%20companies%20like%20Microsoft%20do%20not%20themselves%20manufacture%20any%20physical%20hardware%2C%20it%20should%20be%20possible%20to%20simulate%20them%20entirely%20with%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20didn't%20provide%20more%20details%2C%20and%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20xAI%20did%20not%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Microsoft%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrent%20Mayo%2C%20an%20engineer%20working%20for%20xAI%2C%20retweeted%20Musk's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrok%2C%20Musk's%20AI%2C%20responded%20to%20comments%20on%20X%20and%20said%20that%20AI%20could%20theoretically%20replicate%20Microsoft's%20%26quot%3Bentire%20operations%26quot%3B%20from%20coding%20to%20management%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20company%20is%20now%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDocuments%20from%20the%20United%20States%20Patent%20and%20Trademark%20Office%20also%20show%20that%20a%20mark%20for%20%26quot%3Bmacrohard%26quot%3B%20was%20filed%20on%20August%201%20by%20xAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoug%20Rettew%2C%20a%20trademark%20attorney%20who%20is%20listed%20in%20the%20application%2C%20did%20not%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20lists%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20AI-focused%20goods%20and%20services%20for%20Macrohard%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bdownloadable%20computer%20software%20for%20the%20artificial%20production%20of%20human%20speech%20and%20text%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdownloadable%20computer%20software%20for%20designing%2C%20coding%2C%20running%2C%20and%20playing%20video%20games%20using%20artificial%20intelligence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacrohard%20would%20be%20added%20to%20Musk's%20long%20lineup%20of%20ventures%2C%20which%20he%20either%20partially%20owns%20or%20operates.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20Musk%20is%20simultan