overnment%20has%20reached%20a%20deal%20to%20take%20a%209.9%25%20stake%20in%20Intel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20involves%20the%20US%20investing%20%248.9%20billion%20in%20Intel%20common%20stock.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20talked%20about%20the%20agreement%20on%20Friday%20during%20remarks%20at%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20is%20officially%20investing%20in%20Intel%2C%20a%20remarkable%20development%20and%20a%20rare%20example%20of%20the%20government%20getting%20financially%20involved%20in%20a%20private%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20the%20US%20is%20investing%20%248.9%20billion%20into%20the%20chipmaker%2C%20%26quot%3Breflecting%20the%20confidence%20the%20Administration%20has%20in%20Intel%20to%20advance%20key%20national%20priorities%20and%20the%20critically%20important%20role%20the%20company%20plays%20in%20expanding%20the%20domestic%20semiconductor%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chipmaker%20said%20in%20a%20Friday%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20means%20the%20US%20government%20will%20hold%20a%209.9%25%20stake%20in%20Intel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20%248.9%20billion%20investment%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20%242.2%20billion%20in%20CHIPS%20grants%20Intel%20has%20received%20to%20date%2C%20making%20for%20a%20total%20investment%20of%20%2411.1%20billion%2C%26quot%3B%20Intel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20terms%20of%20today's%20announcement%2C%20the%20government%20agrees%20to%20purchase%20433.3%20million%20primary%20shares%20of%20Intel%20common%20stock%20at%20a%20price%20of%20%2420.47%20per%20share%2C%20equivalent%20to%20a%209.9%20percent%20stake%20in%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Intel%20added.%20%26quot%3BThis%20investment%20provides%20American%20taxpayers%20with%20a%20discount%20to%20the%20current%20market%20price%20while%20enabling%20the%20U.S.%20and%20existing%20shareholders%20to%20benefit%20from%20Intel's%20long-t