as%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-head-shop-cannabis-products-new-york-city-edie-parker-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elifestyle%20brand%20Edie%20Parker%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202010%2C%20and%20by%20about%202017%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20expand.%20We%20had%20made%20a%20name%20for%20ourselves%20with%20handbags%20and%20home%20accessories.%20I%20considered%20expanding%20into%20shoes%20or%20jewelry%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20there%20was%20already%20enough%20of%20that%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20an%20area%20of%20the%20market%20I%20felt%20was%20underserved%3A%20cannabis%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdalwhinnie-farms-aspen-colorado-boutique-cannabis-dispensary-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecannabis%20accessories%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20from%20LA%2C%20and%20though%20I%20live%20in%20New%20York%20City%20now%2C%20I%20go%20back%20to%20California%20a%20lot.%20Every%20time%20I%20went%20into%20a%20dispensary%20in%20California%2C%20I%20felt%20the%20branding%20was%20medicinal%2C%20masculine%2C%20or%20minimalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoms-using-marijuana-stigma-judgment-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enothing%20that%20felt%20catered%20to%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20though%20I%20knew%20from%20personal%20experience%20and%20talking%20to%20other%20women%20that%20cannabis%20can%20be%20great%20for%20everything%20from%20period%20cramps%20to%20spicing%20up%20your%20sex%20life%2C%20to%20just%20unwinding.%20I%20started%20thinking%20about%20how%20Edie%20Parker%20could%20credibly%20enter%20the%20cannabis%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22871f2198-3efe-411d-a60a-a311b8af9b4e%5C%22%3EI%20wanted%20to%20create%20artful%20cannabis%20accessories%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEdie%20Parker%20is%20a%20brand%20born%20out%20of%20a%20good%20time.%20We're%20irreverent%20and%20whimsical.%20My%20approach%20has%20always%20been%20that%20no%20one%20needs%20what%20we're%20selling%2C%20but%20since%20it's%20something%20they%20want%2C%20it%20should%20be%20fun%20and%20playful.%20It%20should%20make%20you%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20how%20I%20feel%20about%20cannabis%2C%20too.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgave-up-alcohol-for-marijuana-made-me-present-patient-parent-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECannabis%20is%20magical%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it's%20something%20that%20should%20spark%20joy.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20about%20medicinal%20use%2C%20but%20if%20you%20just%20want%20to%20get%20high%20and%20watch%20a%20movie%2C%20that's%20fine%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20launch%20Edie%20Parker%20into%20the%20cannabis%20space%20with%20brightly%20colored%20accessories%20like%20pipes.%20These%20were%20art%20%E2%80%94%20something%20meant%20to%20be%20proudly%20displayed%2C%20not%20hidden%20in%20the%20back%20of%20a%20drawer.%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20the%20fear%20and%20stigma%20away%20from%20cannabis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5bed590-05ad-413a-88ae-d6eddb4f6976%5C%22%3EWe%20lost%20some%20customers%2C%20but%20gained%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20start%2C%20I%20underestimated%20how%20hard%20it%20would%20be%20to%20challenge%20the%20conversation%20around%20cannabis.%20I%20was%20naive%20about%20the%20headwinds%20that%20we'd%20face%20as%20a%20brand%20and%20as%20an%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20customers%20would%20come%20into%20the%20Edie%20Parker%20store%20on%20Madison%20Avenue%20and%20buy%20beautiful%20hand-blown%20pipes%20for%20their%20adult%20children.%20But%20over%20time%2C%20the%20people%20who%20don't%20like%20cannabis%20stopped%20looking.%20We%20certainly%20lost%20customers%2C%20and%20despite%20my%20best%20efforts%2C%20the%20cohesion%20between%20the%20brand's%20cannabis%20accessories%20and%20other%20products%20isn't%20totally%20cohesive.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20tapped%20into%20a%20new%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegulatory%20challenges%20are%20a%20whole%20different%20story.%20Edie%20Parker%20isn't%20technically%20a%20plant-touching%20company%2C%20since%20we%20license%20our%20intellectual%20property%20to%20other%20companies.%20That%20spares%20us%20from%20some%20of%20the%20more%20challenging%20tax%20codes%20and%20legal%20implications.%20Still%2C%20I%20worry%20that%20if%20cannabis%20remains%20in%20this%20limbo%20%E2%80%94%20legal%20in%20most%20states%20but%20federally%20illegal%20%E2%80%94%20the%20industry%20won't%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235ef1807-29f0-49a4-9e0a-c2c0240d74ba%5C%22%3EI'm%20proud%20to%20be%20part%20of%20normalizing%20cannabis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20my%20kids%20are%2015%2C%2014%2C%20and%209.%20I%20talk%20to%20them%20about%20cannabis%20the%20way%20I%20talk%20to%20them%20about%20alcohol.%20That's%20the%20obvious%20analogy%20for%20me.%20They%20know%20I%20indulge%20in%20a%20legal%2C%20responsible%20way.%20Still%2C%20I%20don't%20pretend%20there%20are%20no%20risks%20from%20cannabis.%20I%20tell%20my%20kids%20not%20to%20use%20it%20until%20they're%2025%20and%20their%20brains%20have%20stopped%20developing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brett%20Heyman%20and%20kids%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686444adf748d8c055f4c451%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22828%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrett%20Heyman%20talks%20to%20her%20kids%20about%20weed%20the%20same%20way%20she%20talks%20to%20them%20about%20alcohol.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Brett%20Heyman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20into%20this%20business%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-working-with-cannabis-break-down-taboo-for-parents-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunderestimated%20the%20stigma%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20still%20exists%20around%20cannab