lant%20health.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20often%20commutes%20between%20Chennai%20and%20his%20farm%20in%20Kodaikanal.%20His%20plantation%20is%20managed%20by%20four%20permanent%20staff%2C%20with%20around%20ten%20daily%20wage%20workers%20hired%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%2C%20Vimal%20(35)%2C%20explains%3A%20%E2%80%9CEach%20morning%2C%20I%20start%20by%20turning%20on%20the%20music%20system%2C%20then%20collect%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine%20to%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Epanchagavya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20oversee%20the%20drip%20irrigation.%20I%20assign%20tasks%20to%20the%20workers%20and%20monitor%20progress%20throughout%20the%20day.%20We%20usually%20wrap%20up%20by%204%3A30%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELearning%20organic%20practices%20here%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20difficult%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20fulfilling.%20What%20truly%20inspires%20me%20is%20the%20way%20Iyer%20manages%20the%20farm.%20Despite%20his%20age%2C%20he%20remains%20active%20and%20deeply%20involved.%20His%20commitment%20motivates%20all%20of%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Iyer%2C%20this%20shift%20was%20not%20just%20a%20career%20change%20but%20a%20life%20realignment.%20His%20days%20now%20begin%20with%20the%20sunrise%2C%20not%20industrial%20deadlines.%20He%20sips%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F173937%2Fbengaluru-coffee-organic-local-home-grown-plantation-visit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20grown%20on%20his%20own%20farm%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20savouring%20simplicity%20over%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20age%20when%20many%20prefer%20the%20comfort%20of%20retirement%2C%20Iyer%20remains%20dynamic.%20He%20says%20his%20family%20were%20the%20backbone%20of%20his%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20my%20sudden%20decision%20to%20shift%20into%20farming%20initially%20shocked%20them%2C%20their%20support%20soon%20became%20my%20greatest%2