20as%20there%20was%20no%20stability%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neelam%2C%20a%20sewing%20instructor%20at%20Sahaj%20Shakti%20Foundation%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20provides%20vocational%20training%20and%20livelihood%20support%20to%20women%20from%20low-income%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20over%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20her%20routine%20at%20the%20Sahaj%20Shakti%20Foundation%20in%20Gurugram%20was%20marked%20by%20frustration%20and%20uncertainty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20sewing%20instructor%2C%20she%20dedicated%20her%20time%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288638%2Fkashmiri-women-earn-from-crewel-embroidery-initiative-zamruda-bano%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20young%20women%20basic%20embroidery%20and%20hand-stitching%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20hoping%20to%20empower%20them%20with%20a%20means%20to%20earn%20a%20livelihood.%20However%2C%20work%20was%20scarce%20and%20opportunities%20few.%20The%20lack%20of%20steady%20work%20weighed%20heavily%20on%20her%2C%20and%20the%20women%20she%20guided%20often%20found%20themselves%20waiting%20days%20for%20even%20a%20small%20stitching%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20scene%20is%20different.%20Neelam%20and%20nearly%2050%20women%20from%20the%20Sahaj%20Shakti%20Foundation%20are%20engaged%20in%20creating%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%2C%20including%20laptop%20sleeves%2C%20tote%20bags%2C%20wallets%2C%20folders%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20improvement%20worth%20noticing%20is%20the%20material%20they%20work%20with%2C%20which%20is%20discarded%20PVC%20(polyvinyl%20chloride)%20flex%20banners.%20These%20banners%2C%20once%20strung%20up%20across%20streets%20advertising%20everything%20from%20school%20functions%20and%20political%20rallies%20to%20festive%20melas%2C%20were%20typically%20thrown%20away%20after%20brief%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20often%20end%20up%20clogging%20drains%20or%