ains%20sustained%20families%20for%20generations%2C%20keeping%20them%20fed%20and%20healthy.%20But%20today%2C%20shifting%20rainfall%20patterns%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20native%20seeds%20are%20threatening%20not%20just%20the%20harvest%2C%20but%20a%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Pragati%20Abhiyan%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Nasik-based%20nonprofit%2C%20is%20working%20to%20bring%20these%20grains%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20nutrition%20they%20carry%20%E2%80%94%20back%20into%20local%20diets.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20solution%20or%20resilience-building%20effort%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20meet%20the%20specific%20needs%20of%20these%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pranay%20Karuna%2C%20Associate%20Director%20at%20Dasra%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20philanthropic%20foundation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20means%20protecting%20indigenous%20knowledge%2C%20native%20seeds%2C%20and%20natural%20resources.%20From%20planning%20to%20execution%2C%20the%20work%20must%20consider%20all%20the%20different%20challenges%20these%20communities%20face.%20By%20focusing%20on%20farming%20and%20building%20local%20resilience%2C%20Pragati%20Abhiyan%20connects%20the%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%20with%20social%20inequalities%20and%20shows%20why%20solutions%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20local%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dasra%2C%20this%20approach%20is%20not%20new.%20Over%20the%20past%2025%20years%2C%20the%20foundation%20%E2%80%94%20co-founded%20by%20Neera%20Nundy%20and%20Deval%20Sanghavi%20%E2%80%94%20has%20directed%20more%20than%20%24420%20million%20toward%20social%20causes%2C%20supported%20over%201%2C400%20nonprofits%2C%20and%20positively%20impacted%20approximately%20200%20million%20lives.%20One%20of%20its%20most%20effective%20strategies%20has%20been%20to%20build%20alliances%20with%20like-minded%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%2010to19%20Alliance%2C%20which%20empowers%20adolescents%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20girls%20%E2%80%94%20to%20make%20positive%20life%20choices%2C%20to%20%E2%80%98Youth%20Ke%20Bol%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20building%20a%20coalition%20of%20one%20million%20young%20people%20for%20better%20access%20to%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20services%2C%20to%20the%20National%20Faecal%20Sludge%20and%20Septage%20Management%20(NFSSM)%20Alliance%2C%20which%20works%20with%20governments%20and%20municipalities%20on%20liquid%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20collaboration%20has%20always%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Dasra%E2%80%99s%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20rural%20Maharashtra%2C%20Pragati%20Abhiyan%20is%20reviving%20native%20millet%20farming%20to%20fight%20malnutrition%20and%20climate%20stress.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489104%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20rural%20Maharashtra%2C%20Pragati%20Abhiyan%20is%20reviving%20native%20millet%20farming%20to%20fight%20malnutrition%20and%20climate%20stress.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fyoung-indian-farmer-standing-green-millet-2263537057%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20Dasra%2C%20every%20initiative%20has%20been%20rooted%20in%20collaborative%20action%20with%20communities%20at%20the%20centre.%20Through%20conversations%20with%20diverse%20organisations%2C%20we%20realised%20there%20was%20a%20significant%20gap%20in%20work%20around%20climate.%20This%20pushed%20us%20to%20explore%20it%20from%20an%20intersectional%20lens%2C%20focusing%20on%20strengthening%20community%20resilience.%20The%20aim%20was%20to%20shape%20an%20India%20view%2C%20create%20a%20common%20vocabulary%2C%20and%20enable%20multi-stakeholder%20engagement%20on%20climate%20action%20for%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pranay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20explore%20this%2C%20Dasra%20spoke%20with%20almost%20100%20organisations%20in%20its%20network%20that%20were%20working%20in%20climate-adjacent%20areas%2C%20seeking%20to%20understand%20what%20a%20dedicated%20climate%20alliance%20could%20look%20like.%20They%20already%20knew%20how%20to%20build%20alliances%2C%20but%20they%20wanted%20to%20hear%20directly%20from%20partners%20about%20priorities%20within%20the%20climate%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20emerged%20from%20these%20conversations%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98ClimateRISE%20Alliance%20(CRA)%E2%80%99%2C%20launched%20in%20early%202023.%20Bringing%20together%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20think%20tanks%2C%20intermediary%20groups%2C%20and%20funders%2C%20the%20CRA%20was%20established%20with%20support%20from%20Rainmatter%20Foundation%2C%20Oak%20Foundation%2C%20and%20MacArthur%20Foundation.%20Its%20aim%20is%20to%20shape%20%E2%80%9Can%20India%20view%E2%80%9D%20on%20intersectional%20climate%20action%2C%20create%20a%20common%20vocabulary%2C%20and%20enable%20multi-stakeholder%20engagement%20for%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities.%20Today%2C%20about%2070%20organisations%20are%20part%20of