ting-2150933195%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20collaboration%20with%20the%20government%20enables%20impact%20at%20a%20much%20larger%20scale%20than%20one%20organisation%20can%20achieve%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20can%20be%20tricky%20%E2%80%94%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20follow-up%2C%20document%20sharing%2C%20and%20legwork%20involved%20before%20you%20bring%20them%20on%20board.%20With%20Dasra%20as%20the%20secretariat%2C%20the%20CRA%20has%20helped%20us%20collaborate%20more%20effectively%20with%20governments.%20We%E2%80%99re%20able%20to%20work%20across%20multiple%20states%20in%20ways%20that%20would%20have%20been%20far%20harder%20to%20do%20on%20our%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20requests%20can%20also%20stretch%20an%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20capacity.%20Krutika%20recalls%20how%20different%20departments%20have%20asked%20them%20for%20everything%20from%20carbon%20finance%20consultancy%20to%20tracking%20elephants%2C%20setting%20up%20and%20running%20mobile%20science%20laboratories%2C%20developing%20climate-relevant%20curricula%2C%20or%20supplying%20two%20lakh%20saplings%20for%20plantation%20drives.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20CRA%20knows%20exactly%20which%20partner%20to%20approach%20for%20each%20request%2C%20so%20we%20can%20focus%20on%20our%20core%20expertise%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20from%20restoring%20mangroves%20in%20Raigad%20district%20to%20preventing%20deforestation%20in%20Gadchiroli%20district%20%E2%80%94%20often%20involve%20coordination%20with%20other%20CRA%20partners%20like%20Reap%20Benefit%2C%20Technology%20for%20Wildlife%2C%20Grasslands%20Trust%2C%20and%20EarthFokus%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECrafting%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20story%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20nonprofits%2C%20the%20day-to-day%20demands%20of%20their%20work%20leave%20little%20time%20to%20build%20large%2C%20multi-stakeholder%20collaborations.%20%E2%80%9CGenuine%20collaboration%20is%20often%20difficult%20because%20dedicated%20resources%20like%20funding%2C%20staff%2C%20and%20time%20are%20rarely%20available%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prarthana%20Ramesh%20of%20Janaagraha.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEfforts%20like%20outreach%2C%20bringing%20diverse%20stakeholders%20together%2C%20ensuring%20everyone%20is%20aligned%2C%20and%20having%20a%20catalyst%20or%20facilitator%20to%20drive%20the%20project%20forward%20are%20incredibly%20challenging.%20The%20CRA%20has%20effectively%20filled%20this%20gap%20for%20many%20nonprofits%20like%20us.%20It%20has%20enabled%20us%20to%20build%20partnerships%2C%20collaborations%2C%20and%20coalitions%20more%20easily%2C%20without%20constantly%20worrying%20about%20losing%20focus%20or%20struggling%20to%20secure%20funding.%20Consequently%2C%20our%20core%20work%20remains%20unaffected%2C%20and%20the%20alliance%20acts%20as%20an%20enabler%2C%20making%20collaborative%20efforts%20more%20feasible%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20impactful.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-16_11zon-1755612959.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20spotlighting%20local%20realities%20like%20floods%2C%20the%20CRA%E2%80%99s%20Climate%20Narrative%20Hub%20builds%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20climate%20story%20for%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-16_11zon-1755612959.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-16_11zon-1755612959-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-16_11zon-1755612959-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-m